Package: xwayland-satellite-git
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, xwayland, systemd
Conflicts: xwayland-satellite
Provides: xwayland-satellite
Description: Xwayland outside your Wayland (Debian systemd build)
 Grants rootless Xwayland integration to any Wayland compositor
 implementing xdg_wm_base and viewporter. This is particularly useful
 for compositors that do not want to implement rootless Xwayland
 themselves (such as niri).
 .
 This package is compiled from the latest git source with optimizations
 for x86-64-v3 and features native systemd integration (sd-notify).
 Niri will automatically detect and spawn xwayland-satellite when
 X11 clients connect.
